{"vv7:0.1":"Vimanavatthu ","vv7:0.2":"Itthivimana ","vv7:0.3":"Pithavagga ","vv7:0.4":"7. Dutiyanavavimanavatthu ","vv7:1.1":"“Suvannacchadanam navam, ","vv7:1.2":"Nari aruyha titthasi; ","vv7:1.3":"Ogahasi pokkharanim, ","vv7:1.4":"Padmam chindasi panina. ","vv7:2.1":"Kena tetadiso vanno, ","vv7:2.2":"kena te idha mijjhati; ","vv7:2.3":"Uppajjanti ca te bhoga, ","vv7:2.4":"ye keci manaso piya. ","vv7:3.1":"Pucchami tam devi mahanubhave, ","vv7:3.2":"Manussabhuta kimakasi punnam; ","vv7:3.3":"Kenasi evam jalitanubhava, ","vv7:3.4":"Vanno ca te sabbadisa pabhasati”ti. ","vv7:4.1":"Sa devata attamana, ","vv7:4.2":"moggallanena pucchita; ","vv7:4.3":"Panham puttha viyakasi, ","vv7:4.4":"yassa kammassidam phalam. ","vv7:5.1":"“Aham manussesu manussabhuta, ","vv7:5.2":"Purimaya jatiya manussaloke; ","vv7:5.3":"Disvana bhikkhum tasitam kilantam, ","vv7:5.4":"Utthaya patum udakam adasim. ","vv7:6.1":"Yo ve kilantassa pipasitassa, ","vv7:6.2":"Utthaya patum udakam dadati; ","vv7:6.3":"Sitodaka tassa bhavanti najjo, ","vv7:6.4":"Pahutamalya bahupundarika. ","vv7:7.1":"Tam apaga anupariyanti sabbada, ","vv7:7.2":"Sitodaka valukasanthata nadi; ","vv7:7.3":"Amba ca sala tilaka ca jambuyo, ","vv7:7.4":"Uddalaka pataliyo ca phulla. ","vv7:8.1":"Tam bhumibhagehi upetarupam, ","vv7:8.2":"Vimanasettham bhusa sobhamanam; ","vv7:8.3":"Tassidha kammassa ayam vipako, ","vv7:8.4":"Etadisam punnakata labhanti. ","vv7:9.1":"Tena metadiso vanno, ","vv7:9.2":"tena me idha mijjhati; ","vv7:9.3":"Uppajjanti ca me bhoga, ","vv7:9.4":"ye keci manaso piya. ","vv7:10.1":"Akkhami te bhikkhu mahanubhava, ","vv7:10.2":"Manussabhuta yamakasi punnam; ","vv7:10.3":"Tenamhi evam jalitanubhava, ","vv7:10.4":"Vanno ca me sabbadisa pabhasati”ti. ","vv7:11.1":"Dutiyanavavimanam sattamam. "}